Dr. Clarissa Ngiam Ju Cheng Daniel Lee Jian Wen And all relatives and friends. Wake is held at 4 Chestnut Avenue, Singapore 679490 from 21 August 2020, 12nn to 10pm.
Wake registrati­on: https://obits.sg/d/ngiam-tong-dow/4236/en Prayer Service at 8pm.
Cortege leaves on 23 August 2020 (Sunday) for
Mandai Crematoriu­m for a private service.
In view of the current situation, please note that only a maximum of 30 people can be at the wake at one time, we respectful­ly request all those who wish to pay respects to observe the social distancing measures that will be implemente­d at the wake venue.
